name: Arise_Disney Resorts Reservations - Booking Multiple Rooms Package Reservation ~ ADV

audioContentItems.fileTranscript: Thank you for calling Walt Disney World Resorts, where celebrations are our specialty. My name is {Stage Name}. How may I assist you?
Hello, I would like to make a reservation.
I’d be happy to assist you and thank you for choosing Disney as your vacation destination.
May I have your last name and email address?
Callahan, and my email is jcallahan at animail.net.
Thank you, Joan! What dates and how many nights would you like to stay with us?
Checking-In on November 24th, 2025, and Checking-Out on November 30th, 2025.
Thank you, Joan, who will be traveling with you?
My husband Klein.
Thank you, Joan, who else will be traveling with you?
My son, Carrillo.
Thank you, Joan, will there being anyone else traveling with you?
Yes, my daughter Bridget.
Thank you.
Have you decided on which resort you would like to stay at?
Contemporary Resort.
Have you stayed at this resort before?
We have; we love the resort, it’s our favorite.
It’s one of my favorites also. I love how the Monorail travels through the middle of the resort.
Joan, will you need theme park tickets?
Yes, a 6-day ticket with the Park Hopper Plus.
Would you like to include a dining plan?
Yes, I’d like the Disney Dine Plan.
Would you like to include vacation protection in your package for only $95.00 per adult inclusive of children up to 17 years old? It can cover trip cancellation and trip interruption.
No, thanks. We will need 2 rooms as we would like the kids to have their own room.
I will be happy to assist you, please give me a few moments to check the availability.

Would you like to include Memory Maker? Memory Maker is an incredible way to enjoy unlimited digital Disney Photo Pass photos captured at hundreds of locations throughout Walt Disney World Resort—including select attraction and dining locations. The photos are conveniently connected to your online Disney account with a touch of your MagicBand, MagicMobile or Key to the World Card. It is regularly $210, with the advanced price of $185 if purchased at least 3 days prior.
No, thanks.
Will you be flying or driving?
We’re flying.
Will you need a rental car?
No, we don’t need one.

Joan, I do have a few policies to review: A deposit of $200.00 is due on August 20, 2025. The balance is due on October 25, 2025. Modifications within 29 days of arrival are subject to a $50.00 change fee. If you cancel the reservation 29-2 days before arrival, there is a $200 cancellation fee. If you cancel the reservation the day prior to or the day of arrival, the full package price is non-refundable. Gratuity is not included with the Dining Plan. Your Tickets will be valid Monday, November 24th, 2025, to Wednesday, December 23rd, 2025.
No, I don’t.

Joan, I have a reservation for you, Klein Callahan, Bridget Callahan (4 years old), and Carrillo (12 years old). Staying at Disney’s Contemporary Resort in a Garden Wing – Resort View Room with 2 Rooms, Disney Dining Plan and 6 Day Theme Park Ticket with the Park Hopper Plus – Checking in on November 24th, 2025, – Checking out on November 30th, 2025.
Yes, please.
Joan, may I have your credit card number, please?
Thank you.
May I have the expiration month and year, please?
December 2025.
Thank you.
Joan, is the name and address on the reservation the same name and address on your credit card?
Yes.
Joan, would you like to use this credit card for charges incurred during your stay?
Yes.
Joan, your remaining balance is $15,527.38 due 30 days prior to arrival, October 25th, 2025.
Joan, you can link your reservation to MyDisneyExperience.com or the mobile app.
No, thank you.
Joan, is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, thank you!
I have a survey at the end of the call and would greatly appreciate your feedback. Thank you for calling Walt Disney Resorts. We look forward to seeing you in November. Have a Magical Day.
Yes, this sounds perfect.​
Your confirmation number is 27015181.
Your deposit of $200.00 is due on August 20th, 2025, with the remaining balance due 30 days prior to arrival on October 25th, 2025.
Your total reservation is $15,727.38.
Would you like to use your Disney Visa Card for your deposit today?
Our website and app also allow you to book and manage your upcoming ticket, park and dining reservations at Walt Disney World.
You can begin booking your dining reservations 60 days prior to arrival.
Is there a birthday or anything special you will be celebrating during your visit that you would like me to note?
Would you like to secure the reservation for you and your family today? It will only be a $200 deposit the remaining balance will be due 30 days prior to arrival.
Do you have any questions?

Joan, I do have availability, at Disney’s Contemporary Resort, with a Garden Wing – Resort View, with 2 Rooms arriving on November 24th, 2025, checking out on November 30th, 2025, with the Disney Dining Plan and a 6 Day Park Hopper Plus Theme Park Ticket Valid Monday, November 24th, 2025, thru Wednesday, December 3rd, 2025, your total cost will be $15,727.38 Without travel protection, including tax. This would not include the overnight parking fee that will be charged at the resort upon arrival.​

Have your audio and microphone ready.
Congratulations! You have completed this simulation.
